					<th>Event</th>
					<th>Trigger</th>
					<th>What it does</th>
				</tr>
			</thead>
			<tbody>
				<tr>
					<td><code>wb-init.wb-prettify</code></td>
					<td>Triggered manually.</td>
					<td>Initializes the plugin and applies syntax highlighting to the web page's pre and code elements. <b>Note: </b> the prettify plugin will be initialized automatically unless the element is added after the page has already loaded.</td>
				</tr>
				<tr>
					<td><code>prettyprint.wb-prettify</code></td>
					<td>Triggered manually and during plugin initialization.</td>
					<td>Applies syntax highlighting to the web page's pre and code elements.</td>
				</tr>
